{"tid":137954,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨毒遊前記] 高雄有咩好玩？","createTime":"2017-02-28T08:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T01:28:30.000Z","uid":49537,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"231c9df6cef8d5e990a640712e90fab1cec6a149","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"黎緊會一個人去幾日高雄<br />\n大家有無咩地方食物推薦一個人去食去玩?<br />\n到時出發可以出Live post同大家開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9490d0f93e82fbf793cd4f1a52bb8b2001399c9f","tid":137954,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"伸手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eca5d6d3a393059772e93488a41bc1fe2c67e3","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伸手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都搵左啲資料 睇下大家有無咩推薦咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係互相交流下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142b9080ec858644450914749e88f8832327c879","tid":137954,"uid":86815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"駁二藝術特區，旗津彩虹教堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d00d4edc7b28c1a8545fb8eac745cbf21431af","tid":137954,"uid":5762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"食得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推介天使雞扒 塊肉好大又厚但炸得好香脆之餘仲肉嫩多汁<br />\n瑞豐夜市同新堀江商圈都有"},{"pid":"25c05c5f1d1c7c9a89e80c39e4e2e75204b70c59","tid":137954,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>伸手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都搵左啲資料 睇下大家有無咩推薦咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係互相交流下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁睇下舊工廠改建嘅地方啦 個人覺得高雄太城市化  台南正太多"},{"pid":"57e6c711d6c3a788ffbae2c0c7682a54d28c67ce","tid":137954,"uid":27492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:31:18.000Z","msg":"上年都一個人去高雄玩左幾日<br />\n駁二同旗津都唔錯<br />\n不過我覺得旗津好似長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個烤小卷好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a84da0741a263c7f3c5af12477828e310196fc0","tid":137954,"uid":1370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"咁你唔講出黎？<br />\n可唔可以唔好再覆呢啲伸手黨 見到都眼火爆"},{"pid":"5e1e5860081c0ea5fe9f7f4699852b0649ad7d1d","tid":137954,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:47:38.000Z","msg":"旗津食海鮮<br />\n上燈塔"},{"pid":"fda31cd2367b0a7b8a4d7fe130fe9ef32f3a1240","tid":137954,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"打狗祖國領事館"},{"pid":"82db7b39db2f9ad6b743a4794376b47a9d25331b","tid":137954,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:09:00.000Z","msg":"你搵左咪打出黎<br />\n咁先有得討論"},{"pid":"509b8a35c4ad55e59fefe8eb6671840fc6d73245","tid":137954,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打share過台灣推介餐廳post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50e7d5adcfed1ce167a2e1128f67bc0451b5467","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駁二藝術特區，旗津彩虹教堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個我都有興趣!<br />\n駁二好似好多野睇咁樣<br />\n我仲有啲想去大魯閣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc90ebbc84be1b5b69d77797078e893f66b425c6","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推介天使雞扒 塊肉好大又厚但炸得好香脆之餘仲肉嫩多汁<br />\n瑞豐夜市同新堀江商圈都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩! 感謝你! 我到時去搵下先<br />\n聽你咁講都已經流口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a7a4a4ec465027d3edf039f4593fdb2d1b047e","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>伸手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都搵左啲資料 睇下大家有無咩推薦咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係互相交流下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁睇下舊工廠改建嘅地方啦 個人覺得高雄太城市化  台南正太多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為無乜時間呀,所以只逗留係高雄<br />\n搵左個舊鐵橋都好似幾靚幾想去<br />\n但要開始plan下行程先"},{"pid":"562ea8ae25845870f9e4b6096ed0ed2a0289d099","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年都一個人去高雄玩左幾日<br />\n駁二同旗津都唔錯<br />\n不過我覺得旗津好似長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個烤小卷好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你玩左幾多日呀？<br />\n咁睇黎駁二同旗津都真係必去嘅地方<br />\nBtw 你果陣住邊到呀?"},{"pid":"27ac08c63efe8281b7891e50f8dd8750a4fb16c9","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你唔講出黎？<br />\n可唔可以唔好再覆呢啲伸手黨 見到都眼火爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗過去旗津,駁二, 大魯閣, 舊鐵橋, 國立工藝博物館, 壽山觀景台...不過日數唔多要揀幾個點,咪想上黎睇下大家多數推薦啲咩再揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n野食就有諗過去到邊走邊食,不過都努力睇下網上啲人推介緊啲乜"},{"pid":"db3d6900a3ec26790619e56d0a4a61fd7101e0dd","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旗津食海鮮<br />\n上燈塔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈哈 一個人好似食唔到啲咩海鮮<br />\n見人係燈塔影相都幾靚呀!<br />\n應該都會去睇下 thank you"},{"pid":"bf7a005613c35a7eb8f66613ffe393bf8d2a7a32","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打狗祖國領事館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網搵下資料先 thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbdf99c4157c7d6ce1642a08370de36d9fc378f","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你搵左咪打出黎<br />\n咁先有得討論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗過去旗津,駁二, 大魯閣, 舊鐵橋, 國立工藝博物館, 壽山觀景台...<br />\n<br />\n不過仲研究緊路線同時間,我都係想問下大家有無咩推薦並唔是要人幫我安排行程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec71d8ec0afb01feacc948ad717330d5c036fcc9","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有巴打share過台灣推介餐廳post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係？等我search下先! Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2745497b2c02d2f26153d3365b619a4c07e30192","tid":137954,"uid":27492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年都一個人去高雄玩左幾日<br />\n駁二同旗津都唔錯<br />\n不過我覺得旗津好似長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個烤小卷好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你玩左幾多日呀？<br />\n咁睇黎駁二同旗津都真係必去嘅地方<br />\nBtw 你果陣住邊到呀?</blockquote><br />\n玩左四日<br />\n住單人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hostel黎 係真係叫單人房"},{"pid":"a0bd3e4dd33eab86a9ddc6289cd07a5ca432c080","tid":137954,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"打狗可以唔駛去,無乜野睇"},{"pid":"95c37ee9ed86bec9f764b70afe081418981fe0ce","tid":137954,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>旗津食海鮮<br />\n上燈塔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈哈 一個人好似食唔到啲咩海鮮<br />\n見人係燈塔影相都幾靚呀!<br />\n應該都會去睇下 thank you</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少有少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dcef99429ce4273748c09abc5db9c8ecc38951","tid":137954,"uid":49537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T01:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上年都一個人去高雄玩左幾日<br />\n駁二同旗津都唔錯<br />\n不過我覺得旗津好似長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個烤小卷好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你玩左幾多日呀？<br />\n咁睇黎駁二同旗津都真係必去嘅地方<br />\nBtw 你果陣住邊到呀?</blockquote><br />\n玩左四日<br />\n住單人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hostel黎 係真係叫單人房</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都book左單人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你覺得好唔好住呀?<br />\n見人話隔音好差,係咪真係聽到晒隔離啲人做乜架?<br />\n<br />\n你覺得高雄好唔好玩呀咁？"}]}